Françoise Morhange https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fran%C3%A7oise_Morhange 0 Françoise Morhange (1915–1984) was a French actress. In 1980, she starred in Le Voyage en douce under director Michel Deville. Françoise_Morhange ( 1915 – 1984 ) was a_French_actress . In 1980 , she starred in Le_Voyage en douce under director_Michel_Deville .
